      "content": "It's not recommended to drink grapefruit juice with atorvastatin. Grapefruit juice can interact with the medication, reducing its effectiveness and possibly increasing the risk of side effects. To minimize interactions, consider avoiding grapefruit juice for at least a few hours after taking your medication. If you're concerned, consult your doctor or pharmacist for guidance.",
